{"tid":37893,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"車輛過戶手續程序一問？","createTime":"2016-12-13T15:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T02:32:53.000Z","uid":23947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87317a8e6621448b9111a863abc04497a832c1fe","tid":37893,"uid":23947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"小弟睇岩左架二手車(1137的神車)，即場落埋細訂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而舊車主話工作繁忙唔多方便現身，交比新車主(即是細佬我) 負責。小弟咩都唔識，有無巴打講解下程序？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s. 裝到佢攝左幾張牛肉乾起中控台雜物格，點知道佢交左罰款未？如未交會唔會過落新車主度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f3d5970760d683525054edb9a58330ebc205ef","tid":37893,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548fde37f259a3555b030ff719bf56726350d8d6","tid":37893,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"未清罰款好似過唔到戶<br />\n<br />\n只要佢肯比牌簿正本你同埋係過戶份form到簽左名,咁佢唔使出現都可以<br />\n<br />\n琴日先過完戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e23441e800ea6ef297e44fb923f24680dec8d1","tid":37893,"uid":2769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:28:22.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"6c315ccaa1da35c032592365f8fe882e7042a2a4","tid":37893,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"Echo?"},{"pid":"9632484e919459a8f391639457ac8af11d7d1180","tid":37893,"uid":23947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未清罰款好似過唔到戶<br />\n<br />\n只要佢肯比牌簿正本你同埋係過戶份for